    <h3>District Information</h3>
    <p>The Boulder Valley School District offers an impressive well-rounded course list and an extensive array of programs and extra-curricular activities that aim to please each student's interests. The district also provides honors courses in all academic areas and an incredibly comprehensive Advanced Placement program. They are consistently ranked in the top 3 school systems in the state of Colorado, leading in student performance two years in a row. The city prides itself on its reputation for its academic excellence. In fact, it has been national recognized in the reputable Forbes magazine for being the "The Most Educated City in America," in 2008.</p>
